Achievements.Name: Deliverer of Salvation
Achievements.Description: Proof of clearing 5 side quests. It is a fine beginning, but the journey is still long.

Achievements.Name: Angel of Salvation
Achievements.Description: Proof of clearing 25 side quests. It is a great feat to lead so many souls to salvation.

Achievements.Name: Seed Collector
Achievements.Description: Proof of a brave warrior who has managed to claim 50 soul seeds from the Chaos.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Passenger
Achievements.Description: Proof of riding upon all of the great monorail lines that cross this shrinking world.

Achievements.Name: Globetrotter
Achievements.Description: Proof of building strong bridges to span the depths between continents, making all the world one.

Achievements.Name: A Helping Hand
Achievements.Description: Proof of clearing 25 quests that have appeared writ on the Canvas of Prayers.

Achievements.Name: Novice Swordsmith
Achievements.Description: Proof of improving your first weapon. Did you make something worthy?

Achievements.Name: Novice Shieldsmith
Achievements.Description: Proof of improving your first shield. Use it wisely to guard yourself.

Achievements.Name: Novice Synthesist
Achievements.Description: Proof of synthesizing your first ability. Did it prove useful?

Achievements.Name: Novice Craftsman
Achievements.Description: Proof of upgrading your first accessory. Did you find the experience thrilling?

Achievements.Name: Novice Stylist
Achievements.Description: Proof of customizing your first schema. Continue on this path to find your own style.

Achievements.Name: Novice Artist
Achievements.Description: Proof of customizing the color of one of your garb. Let your true colors shine through.

Achievements.Name: Expert Swordsmith
Achievements.Description: Proof of modifying weapons 30 times.

Achievements.Name: Expert Shieldsmith
Achievements.Description: Proof of modifying shields 30 times.

Achievements.Name: Expert Synthesist
Achievements.Description: Proof of synthesizing abilities 30 times.

Achievements.Name: Expert Craftsman
Achievements.Description: Proof of upgrading accessories 30 times.

Achievements.Name: Expert Stylist
Achievements.Description: Proof of obtaining 30 different garb.

Achievements.Name: Hero of Might
Achievements.Description: Proof of victory over 100 foes in battle.

Achievements.Name: Hero of Glory
Achievements.Description: Proof of victory over 300 foes in battle.

Achievements.Name: Hero of Legend
Achievements.Description: Proof of victory over 500 foes in battle.

Achievements.Name: Fatal Impact
Achievements.Description: Proof of dealing damage so great that it goes beyond all reason or expectation.

Achievements.Name: Seeing Stars
Achievements.Description: Proof of staggering enemies 50 times with fearsome attacks. Do not ever let them rest!

Achievements.Name: Miracle of Light
Achievements.Description: Proof of one who has used 50 EP.

Achievements.Name: Perfect Timing
Achievements.Description: Proof of successfully guarding against an enemy's attack with perfect timing.

Achievements.Name: The Savior's Descent
Achievements.Description: Proof of one who has mastered the basics of this world and begun a great journey.

Achievements.Name: The Hope of a Promise
Achievements.Description: Proof of one who has seen through the dark mysteries that lurked in Luxerion, bringing justice.

Achievements.Name: Hope at the Edge of Despair
Achievements.Description: Proof of one who has stood upon the stage in glittering Yusnaan, bringing peace to the Patron.

Achievements.Name: The Mystery of the Holy Clavis
Achievements.Description: Proof of one who has made it through the Dead Dunes to find ancient treasure.

Achievements.Name: An Appetite for Chaos
Achievements.Description: Proof of one who has visited the temple that towers over the Wildlands and touched the great Chaos.

Achievements.Name: A Legend from Times Past
Achievements.Description: Proof of the true savior, who overthrew even the god of light to lead the people to a new world.

Achievements.Name: Beyond Thirteen
Achievements.Description: Proof of making the impossible possible by using Eradia to bring the world a 14th day.

Achievements.Name: A Father, a Son, and a Chocobo
Achievements.Description: Proof of helping a father and son reunite, bringing back a smile that seemed long lost.

Achievements.Name: The Chocobo's Savior
Achievements.Description: Proof of nursing the holy chocobo back to full health among the rich pastures of the Wildlands.

Achievements.Name: Lizard Lariat
Achievements.Description: Proof of hunting down more than 30 lizards in the shifting sands of the Dead Dunes.

Achievements.Name: Crimson Rebirth
Achievements.Description: Proof of restoring a sword, once broken, to its former glory and power.

Achievements.Name: Queen of the Arena
Achievements.Description: Proof of achieving victory in the lists of the Battle Arena 10 times.

Achievements.Name: Unearthly Apothecary
Achievements.Description: Proof of obtaining an elixir. It's so rare that it seems almost a waste to use it, doesn't it?

Achievements.Name: Holy Garb of Destruction
Achievements.Description: Proof of obtaining the ultimate garb, imbued with destructive magic.

Achievements.Name: Monster Bane
Achievements.Description: Proof of mastering all creation and conquering even the Ultimate Lair.

Achievements.Name: Desert Dragonslayer
Achievements.Description: Proof of victory over the dragon Aeronite who brought terror to the Dead Dunes.

Achievements.Name: Harbinger of Death
Achievements.Description: Proof of defeating your first Last One, the final specimen of a species on the verge of extinction.

Achievements.Name: Goddess of Death
Achievements.Description: Proof of defeating 10 Last Ones, exterminating forever 10 different species of monster.
